snippet.title: PSYCHO DEAD - Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam :  https://store.steampowered.com/app/3018390/PSYCHO_DEAD
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
"Psycho Dead" is a third-person survival horror game centered on a mysterious girl with psychic powers, who must escape a secret laboratory infested with grotesque and monstrous creatures. Explore a sci-fi setting filled with mystery and danger, where terror awaits at every corner, and discover the truth behind the horrific incident. 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
